{"tid":2114302,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"天水圍發生咩事","createTime":"2020-07-18T17:04:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-18T17:20:34.000Z","uid":211994,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"c9e20473192cd27fafbe9a94d70439ea9566dec3","tid":2114302,"uid":211994,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T17:04:35.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"x-large\"><span class=\"gold\">又斬人又圍毆<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家小心啲</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BshP6Cw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBshP6Cw.jpg&h=80d00528&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hn78CKc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHn78CKc.jpg&h=567d7802&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/92RtCKd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F92RtCKd.jpg&h=d44b3d92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n#天水圍<br />\n0022 天恆邨於約20分鐘前曾發生懷疑斬人事故，早前據報曾有超過2架衝鋒車及2架救護車到現場。<br />\n<br />\n目前有2架衝鋒車及軍裝警員落地調查事件。現場街坊表示傷者手臂被斬傷，有數個傷口，傷勢頗深。<br />\n<br />\n據警員透露早前曾有數名人士從車上跳下並攻擊傷者，其後乘車離去。傷者被救護送往醫院治理，警方正調查襲擊者身份。<br />\n<br />\n感謝現場街坊提供傷勢照片。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"x-large\"><p class=\"left\">冇幾耐又有一單</p></span></span><br />\n<br />\n#天水圍 0057<br />\n天醫近臭河段發生打鬥事件<br />\n據街坊指 有為數10-20個黑衫青年向2位男子施襲<br />\n現場有血跡遺留 <br />\n2位受傷男子由友人扶持往天醫方向離開<br />\n10-20黑衫青年往天北方向離開"},{"pid":"d153c8e9267bed1c77351431783852c80d06041e","tid":2114302,"uid":26189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T17:05:20.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f3b9f229880545af8fe5e558c9648c2773a44e1","tid":2114302,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-18T17:05:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8d0506cc3dceb32